headline.main: Collective Health, Insurance Services Start-Up Focused on Employers, Raises $81 Million

byline.original: By MICHAEL J. de la MERCED

snippet: Collective Health, which provides tools to help companies with their employer-provided insurance, has now raised a total of $119 million from investors like Google Ventures..
